headline: This Unstoppable Dividend-Paying Growth Stock Is Up More Than 260% in 5 Years. Here's Why It Just Hit an All-Time High.
summary: Deere & Company stock leaped to a new all-time high after its earnings and forecast were good, given the challenging economic environment.  The equipment manufacturer continues to generate strong margins that support long-term growth.  Deere is raking in free cash flow to fuel stock buybacks and dividend increases.
